phantom_task.py
phantom/psiphon-tunnel-core
phantom/psiphon_data/
phantom/remote_server_list*

# Reports (task output artifacts)
reports/

# ============================================================
# EXPLICITLY TRACKED (do NOT ignore these):
#   - logs/              → operational logs, committed for history
#   - memory/            → agent memory, committed for history
#   - *.log files inside logs/ are tracked (override below)
# ============================================================
!logs/
!logs/**
!memory/
!memory/**